 />\n就算佢呢刻留你都只係因為未搵到第二個又唔想身邊少左個人<br />\n逝去感情如何留得住"},{"pid":"c4217779c6d0dea76f018b70a9cad2c0f2622431","tid":306651,"uid":76926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:21:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽返首好彩分手</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喂 唔駛咁愁喎朋友<br />\n一段感情梗有佢完嘅時候架<br />\n佢肯同你分手 你應該走夾唔抖喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你咪為佢費神 你當為己為人<br />\n你有冇聽聞得饒人處且饒人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa57ad820f98af6bc603f089aa95b31a6c09b13c","tid":306651,"uid":126260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:21:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係唔係想真分手<br />\n只係想佢哄、想佢改變？<br />\n你因住佢真係答 好 分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係，但佢從來唔會氹我。次次我嬲唔理佢，最後都係我搵返佢。"},{"pid":"8c2aa1a5bbe16750ef8ccf80a7a6703a45c1fd89","tid":306651,"uid":123175,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:21:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係唔係想真分手<br />\n只係想佢哄、想佢改變？<br />\n你因住佢真係答 好 分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好on9啦唔該<br />\n想人氹就開聲講<br />\n好日都唔提分手<br />\n無啦啦提出黎基本上都覺得你認真<br />\n<br />\n對聽嘅人黎講<br />\n分手從來唔係提出黎討論<br />\n而只係通知<br />\n<br />\n你都想分，唔通對方可以單方面唔畀分咩<br />\n<br />\n唔好攞黎玩唔該，一啲都唔好玩"},{"pid":"f4b1272c1f175c83904b2010c4618c766c5583f7","tid":306651,"uid":50483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:21:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好辛苦想分手。但未下定決心分手，好驚佢覆話「好，分手！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你估「好，分手！」呢。句<br />\n係為咗邊個講吖嗱</blockquote><br />\n驚佢真係厭左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌厭咗 唔要你 好正常</blockquote><br />\n唔想分手唔好提分手<br />\n提分手嘅結果一般都係分</blockquote><br />\n好想佢話唔好，唔分，仲愛我</blockquote><br />\n咁咪係囉 自己又要唔捨得 又要提分手 <br />\n有邊對情侶 唔想對方放自己係第一位<br />\n當初追你一定係好關心你架啦<br />\n時間耐左 大家做既野都唔同<br />\n每日返工受完氣做完野<br />\n仲要去應酬你 唔岩心意就話hea"},{"pid":"d6bb58cdfdfa171bc30fdbda64558fdc88b661e6","tid":306651,"uid":126260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:21:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一齊左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n一年"},{"pid":"b0640bc438a32df436ea0d23ac91a45a25f7449a","tid":306651,"uid":58614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:22:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好辛苦想分手。但未下定決心分手，好驚佢覆話「好，分手！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你估「好，分手！」呢。句<br />\n係為咗邊個講吖嗱</blockquote><br />\n驚佢真係厭左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌厭咗 唔要你 好正常</blockquote><br />\n男人係咪真係個個都會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樣，波，腳，性格 <br />\n是但有樣唔掂 屌完好快厭 <br />\n信我 9成屌厭咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e97564943cc6590bd160ee05e46859d47f73e2f","tid":306651,"uid":123175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T17:24:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好辛苦想分手。但未下定決心分手，好驚佢覆話「好，分手！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你估「好，分手！」呢。句<br />\n係為咗邊個講吖嗱</blockquote><br />\n驚佢真係厭左我<img